bu akış ile değiştirebilirim.

API-
@when(parsers.parse('the user creates a note with title "{title}"'))
def create_note(title, notes_client):
    context["response"] = notes_client.create_note(title)


UI----
@when(parsers.parse('the user creates a note with title "{title}"'))
def create_note(title, notes_page):
    notes_page.open_create_form()
    notes_page.enter_title(title)
    notes_page.click_create()


